{"tid":2479077,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"BRAVO COOKIES 拖員工一個月糧","createTime":"2021-04-07T14:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:14:25.000Z","uid":205080,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e10099014f739efbf4495774c3c022e6a239e0","tid":2479077,"uid":205080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"小妹由2月中開始喺沙田新城市 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">Bravo Cookies 唔好港嘢</span></span> 度翻Part time (無簽過任何合約)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU4AFWaf3gqdLTBby2ELhYNmrfTCceeMmjtApeuGo7AMu?filename=KnKEdFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnKEdFw.jpg&h=9ad54e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始鋪頭負責人<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">口頭承諾</span></span>左每個月逢5號同20號出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但第二次出糧嘅時候（ 05 / 03 / 2021 ）我check銀行發現無出到，事關有啲同事收到有啲同事收唔到，以為可能係銀行問題，就無即時問負責人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知過隔左成個星期都收唔到，已經即刻問負責人咩事，但仍然收唔到，所有有一直追問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始我都恭恭敬敬有禮貌地問佢，後尾發覺佢根本無比過一個確實嘅回覆比我！<br />\n只係一直<strong><span class=\"x-large\">聲稱</span></strong>話有追老闆同處理緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最後都忍唔住自己嘅怒火喺翻工嘅群入面屌鳩間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到後尾先講話銀行reject左出糧嘅幾條數，要去銀行搞bilibala<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但直到今日，4月7號我依然未收到我份人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問可以點做？<br />\nWhatsapp對話如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQu4AzJKaVqBVfDDxR24qS8jx9ToKzeBnMo6zQxxLX9KQ?filename=8gfsnYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gfsnYx.jpg&h=7074868d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPBPybej7dAPei8gX3GoSBcm6v1bDxVBFsBvCGTxTy6VR?filename=DR6Gsqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDR6Gsqd.jpg&h=ce1d96cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf9nBRVNhVm4eZ4Jkb2a9JuQp6PqfkCWmsP25TJxRryns?filename=oZCiuDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZCiuDA.jpg&h=a66fcd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTyARp599d76H1zWQRYXubYWeCnQPpd2McBYX7UgYPD2S?filename=pd9diwV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpd9diwV.jpg&h=326f259d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdehE9ogwo7Ucfda3yL7AhZfKzNdT8LatyvY8YUhVbwxS?filename=xM0PBiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxM0PBiC.jpg&h=d7232632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVkXLrHSNAkz7szKt78LXYbD34ZEiT3Jo1NY4r29GKHCh?filename=YruEd5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYruEd5i.jpg&h=6eb39084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU7utffA4A7jCtQ5RQqvwRNzWzHfgjtL1SkRpChuwuUpB?filename=AXA0HYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXA0HYE.jpg&h=6bcc8a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfFwwLbTqmYNeTgyRN5XpvGKM2rdpXq2x3jU1q5o2iyWR?filename=7GEQkLm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GEQkLm.jpg&h=10e4b5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你出cash又好，cancel銀行個payment再repay又好<br />\n真係有心解決嘅就點都有方法出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係好似而加咁無責任感，咁肉酸無了期咁拖人成個月糧<br />\n如果唔係我不斷主動死lur住問，負責人亦無諗住主動話我知到底我份糧去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋Bravo Cookies係under <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">港嘢茶檔</span></span>㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地扯：<br />\n1. 灣仔譚臣道8號威利商業大廈地下<br />\n2. 九龍城侯王道22號地下<br />\n出糧公司：<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">Goldford Group Limited</span></span><br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYkN2SL3MZjdrvSetdC14hc7gmAQJdjrn86SveuDsqLLX?filename=488BgaJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F488BgaJ.jpg&h=e6c1f52a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一個老闆： LAU L** C*** ANGELA<br />\n希望大家唔好幫襯以上嘅無良食肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦唔好喺以上嘅黑心公司翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想講多一句，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">拖糧死全家！！！！！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a36e9705d221ec9cc57c7ca6b93c454e22d49a69","tid":2479077,"uid":312254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正仆街<br />\n推"},{"pid":"4daedc70915b8c449cc3793ac3e5e77058e6bd3c","tid":2479077,"uid":205080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5da6ae86dc75d023027304451aa094ede16ef42","tid":2479077,"uid":205080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8011ff4456d036642293393651924ed7efb8d4a3","tid":2479077,"uid":205080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:20:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63c5d9dae1b10b62617ba6155a9bc1a8c41d0ee","tid":2479077,"uid":2